罗斯总统普京 9 月告诉记者，俄方将于 11 月参加在印度尼西亚巴厘岛举行的二十国集团峰会，但普京补充说，他尚未决定是否参加此次峰会。 （环球网） 「普京和泽连斯基都同意」"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "87 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/558188719"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0IiYm2rZuxjSgQAxoIODYzMjQ3NjYgjIyEmgYwBjhNQBZyCTU1ODE4ODcxOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1665241591.6953256", "card_id": "Q_544655159", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 59}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《隐入尘烟》里面海清可能是什么病？治疗需要多少钱？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-f83aa46cc7b04ecd8f9bab94cac45030_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "87 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/544655159"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IiYm2rZuxjSgQAxoIODMzMTcxNTYgkKHmlgYwAji/AUAXcgk1NDQ2NTUxNTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1665241591.6960082", "card_id": "Q_556006932", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 43}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么现在的 iPhone 没有当年的 iPhone 那种惊艳了，是手机发展到尽头了没法突破了吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当年第一次买 iPhone4s，简直惊为天人，觉得这才是真正的手机 后来一直到 5S 、 6S 、 8P 等 iPhoneX 发布的时候因为价格太高没有购买，但是现在看有些同事在用，在当时看来不错，同事说用了好多年一直很流畅，当时刘海屏真的很惊艳，我甚至还在转转买了一部二手当备用 但感觉从 iPhone11 开始就有点挤牙膏了，到现在 iPhone14，竟然丝毫没有新意，就连灵动岛也只是 UI 动画，难道 iPhone 的变革式创新真的到头了。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-825782a303f3e9c75b5a29575a72b197_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "86 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/556006932"}}, "at